<input class="js-input-hidden-f-id" type="hidden" value="<%= fId %>" />
<input type="hidden" class="js-input-hidden-food-category-data" value="<%= foodCategory2List %>" />


<div class="wrapper food detail">
    <h1 class="title">음식 상세</h1>

    <div class="form-box">
        <p>*음식 이름</p>
        <input type="text" class="js-input-name default" />
    </div>

    <div class="form-box">
        <p>*음식 키워드 (검색어 노출용)</p>
        <div class="js-div-keyword-list keyword-list">
            <div class="js-div-keyword-add keyword-add">
                <input class="js-input-keyword-add default" type="text" />
                <button class="js-button-keyword-add default"><i class="fal fa-plus"></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-box">
        <p>급여가능유무</p>
        <select class="js-select-edible default">
            <option value="Y" selected>가능</option>
            <option value="N">불가능</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    
    <div class="form-box">
        <p>상위 카테고리</p>
        <select class="js-select-category1 default">
            <% for (let i = 0; i < foodCategory1List.length; i++) { %>
                <option value="<%= foodCategory1List[i].fc1_id %>"><%= foodCategory1List[i].fc1_name %></option>
            <% } %>
        </select>
    </div>

    <div class="form-box">
        <p>하위 카테고리</p>
        <select class="js-select-category2 default">
            
        </select>
    </div>

    <div class="form-box">
        <p>음식 썸네일 이미지 (클릭하여 업로드)</p>
        <div class="image-box">
            <form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data"><input class="js-input-thumbnail" name="image" type="file" accept="image/jpeg,image/png" /></form>
            <div class="js-div-thumbnail thumbnail"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-box">
        <p>급여방법 및 주의사항</p>
        <textarea class="js-textarea-desc default"></textarea>
    </div>

    <div class="form-box">
        <p>음식과 연관된 "영양소"</p>
        <div class="js-div-nutrient-list relationship-list">
            <button class="js-button-nutrient-add relationship-add default"><i class="fal fa-plus"></i></button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
        <button class="js-button-cancel default">취소</button>
        <button class="js-button-food-save default">음식 저장</button>
    </div>
</div>
